A researcher in a softly-lit observation room sits behind a one-way mirror, intently watching a person on the other side who is clicking through a computer interface, their face illuminated by the screen's glow. The observer holds a clipboard covered in handwritten notes, leaning forward with genuine curiosity. Warm amber lighting fills the observation booth while cool blue monitor light spills from the testing area. The scene is rendered in Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, gentle gradients, and expressive character details that convey both concentration and human connection. Potted plants and cozy details fill the corners of the observation room, giving it a welcoming feel despite its technical purpose.
